natSocketChannelImpl.cc: Reverse logic for DISABLE_JAVA_NET.

2003-02-21  Michael Koch  <konqueror@gmx.de>

	* gnu/java/nio/natSocketChannelImpl.cc:
	Reverse logic for DISABLE_JAVA_NET. Thanks to Krister Walfridsson
